<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Viacom downgraded - sources.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Viacom downgraded - sources.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Oppenheimer and Co downgraded Viacom Inc to market performer from buy, market sources said.</p>
<p>-- The analyst was not immediately available for comment.</p>
<p>-- Earlier, Viacom said it plans a public offering next year of a new class of Viacom stock that will track the performance of its Blockbuster Entertainment chain of video stores.</p>
<p>-- The stock fell four to 26-3/8.</p>
</text>
